descriptionHtml:
=================
Details:
=================

Whenever you initiate a conversation with Sheogorath, potatoes will fly everywhere! Inspired by this quote from Arthmoor: \"This is only going to be an issue if you have a room filled with hundreds of potatoes. Since no vanilla interior does, and no sane modder around will do such a thing either, it isn\'t going to be an issue for the 5 or 6 you DO find in these places.\"

Let it be known! I AM NO SANE MODDER.

Note: this mod uses the placeatme command. I\'m not sure if the Papyrus version causes the problems the command has in past games, but it might be a good idea to keep your interaction with Sheogorath to a minimum.

This mod is JUST FOR FUN.
author: ishmaeltheforsaken and Sheogorath and Oscar Wilde
